  "intent_summary": "Compute sales growth (%) for the most recent 4 distinct weeks (R4W) vs the immediately preceding 4 distinct weeks (P4W) by campus (child) account type, and compare each child account type growth to national growth over the same windows. Include absolute sales for both windows and a Higher/Lower vs nation indicator. Use week_end_date anchored to MAX(week_end_date) in data_867.",
